{"tid":1291172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以武制暴係人之根本","createTime":"2019-07-06T18:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:38:20.000Z","uid":264457,"like":84,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"44320122f10361050bc7e9c635e75fba0967168c","tid":1291172,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:17:45.000Z","msg":"之前出左post叫遊行人士要被人打要還拖。<br />\n宜家見到出面又有人出淡風要拎光環，我唔知佢地有冇上過前線，有冇經歷過雨革，有冇被人打過。<br />\n以一個正常人，有人打你你唔打番轉頭係好唔合理既行為，係明知黑警唔會執法既同時，你既「被打」係白白既犧牲。<br />\n點解宜家周不時有一兩個人就可以如入無人之境，如趙雲般去抗釁我地，係因為佢地知佢地打人後會被人安全送走。<br />\n啲其他示威者唔會對佢點，因為佢地要拎光環，但被人打既就白白受傷。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我一直強調要要合適武力制服佢。係要增加佢地搞事既成本。</strong></span></span><br />\n我建議聽日有人搞事，圍觀既圍起佢先，扮勸架咁拉住佢，開遮既開遮，由後面既出陰招，出腳既出服去招呼佢地，之後散開比警犬拉佢走。<br />\n被打還拖係人之根本，話唔還人既我希望被打既會係你地。<br />\n14年到19年都係咁撚on9，連自己或身邊既人被人打都保護唔到既，你地點出來抗爭？"},{"pid":"9fc835bc9965c945988ea92b5204f754a21b8b8a","tid":1291172,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:20:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"55f8beb3d467a5740a98541d9b7214516e49e486","tid":1291172,"uid":264457,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:25:30.000Z","msg":"重推，唔好俾啲keyboard fighter 帶風向。<br />\n真係好懷疑啲書生軍師係咪可以會出來帶頭比人打不還手。<br />\n係既我唔介意作圍觀者睇戲。<br />\n我想睇下你點攞光環。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90e862a22b3b4474227777fb689b6d74679bbf7","tid":1291172,"uid":267044,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afe81835aa75aaaa542c4230f8a92c66f2cf13b9","tid":1291172,"uid":202730,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦p牌<br />\n註冊日期: 6/18/2019"},{"pid":"725de07feddf7d26207cf9662c0996196c36d0a3","tid":1291172,"uid":264457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"負評狗出來講下野啦<br />\n又係啲比黑警拉？一拳超人一出手就會打死人論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗你擔心下自己被人打死好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236987de7b55be650a7ccd26fdaa96332d2e5d92","tid":1291172,"uid":264457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a90e862a22b3b4474227777fb689b6d74679bbf7","tid":1291172,"uid":267044,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:30:03.000Z","msg":"P牌係咪都係你呀？<br />\n繼續推post啦"},{"pid":"ae3027550f77da876137bcc2239dda6219f60551","tid":1291172,"uid":222620,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>p</strong>"},{"pid":"dafda4ad52e062b4b9541cf8e7624d6f2e867695","tid":1291172,"uid":264457,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"afe81835aa75aaaa542c4230f8a92c66f2cf13b9","tid":1291172,"uid":202730,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦p牌<br />\n註冊日期: 6/18/2019"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:31:23.000Z","msg":"點呀, 係連登扮老屎忽既咪去高登度講lor, 睇下係高登邊個係註冊日期耐啲？"},{"pid":"12a03ddaacd04e106ebbe690bfc7f848ad30a754","tid":1291172,"uid":202730,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"dafda4ad52e062b4b9541cf8e7624d6f2e867695","tid":1291172,"uid":264457,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"afe81835aa75aaaa542c4230f8a92c66f2cf13b9","tid":1291172,"uid":202730,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦p牌<br />\n註冊日期: 6/18/2019"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:31:23.000Z","msg":"點呀, 係連登扮老屎忽既咪去高登度講lor, 睇下係高登邊個係註冊日期耐啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好大個官威呀"},{"pid":"6cfe62cbaa758e6140c3b896e08458714927d560","tid":1291172,"uid":49184,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T18:34:13.000Z","msg":"上面反對的, 1個point都比唔撚到出來<br />\n淨係識得屌OP p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.